CT/55      V0.3      V0.3 BRANCH               + ACTIVITY UML FTRS       EPIC
Add new activity uml features (see CT/60)

ACTION NODES
See pre-requisite task CT/63. When user clicks to place an action node, it will
result in minibuffer being pre-populated with `group ` and will
create the rect + 2 text elements with that group name and a Group XML editing
tab open by default and the top text selected first.
